# HW1 - Q2 Image Classification (Russian Wildlife)

This repository contains code to reproduce Q2 (Image Classification) for the assignment.
Run the three required experiments (scratch CNN baseline; ResNet-18 finetune without augmentation; ResNet-18 finetune with augmentation) and the DINOv2/timm feature extraction with t-SNE + KMeans.

Seed used throughout: `2023090`.

## Quick commands (run from repo root)

1. Create splits (if you have dataset folder structure):
```bash
python -m src.dataset --root path/to/wildlife_dataset --make-splits --out_csv_dir data/splits --seed 2023090

Plot class distributions (required for Q2.1.c):

python scripts/plot_class_distribution.py

Scratch CNN (10 epochs, baseline, Q2.2):

python -m src.train_scratch --train_csv data/splits/train.csv --val_csv data/splits/val.csv --epochs 10 --batch_size 64 --out_dir outputs/scratch_baseline --wandb --wandb_project "HW1_RussianWildlife" --run_name "scratch_10ep_run"

ResNet-18 finetune without augmentation (Q2.3):

python -m src.train_finetune --train_csv data/splits/train.csv --val_csv data/splits/val.csv --epochs 10 --batch_size 32 --out_dir outputs/resnet_no_aug --wandb --wandb_project "HW1_RussianWildlife" --run_name "resnet18_no_aug"

ResNet-18 finetune with augmentation (Q2.4):

python -m src.train_finetune --train_csv data/splits/train.csv --val_csv data/splits/val.csv --epochs 10 --batch_size 32 --out_dir outputs/resnet_with_aug --wandb --wandb_project "HW1_RussianWildlife" --run_name "resnet18_with_aug" --augment

Feature extraction + PCA->t-SNE + KMeans (Q3.2.d):

python -m src.extract_features --csv data/splits/val.csv --out_dir outputs/features --model dinov2_vits14 --k_clusters 8
Deliverables for Report

outputs/plots/train_class_dist.png and val_class_dist.png (Q2.1.c)

training curves (W&B or exported PNGs)

confusion matrices and misclassified_grid PNGs for each model

t-SNE plot and cluster examples

augmentation sample images (if running finetune with --augment)
